                     </ns0:supportDesc>
                     <ns0:layoutDesc>
                        <ns0:layout>
                           <ns0:p>The left side of the text and its margin is completely preserved from L. 4 onward; all other margins are unknown. The text appears to wrap, e.g. from L. 4 to L. 5 where the break is between syllables.</ns0:p>
                           <ns0:rs ana="#execution.engraved" ref="https://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/3.html">engraved</ns0:rs>
