           <ns0:app><ns0:note>C. adds two speculatively restored lines before the first preserved line: <ns0:supplied reason="lost">&#960;&#949;&#960;&#961;&#8118;&#963;&#952;&#945;&#953; &#916;&#943;&#969;&#957;&#953; &#964;&#959;&#8166; &#948;&#949;&#8150;&#957;&#959;&#962; &#964;&#8056; &#964;&#959;&#8166; &#948;&#949;&#8150;&#957;&#959;&#962; &#964;&#959;&#8166; &#948;&#949;&#8150;&#957;&#959;&#962; &#7952;&#957;</ns0:supplied></ns0:note></ns0:app>
