           <ns0:app loc="8"><ns0:note>C. interprets the monogram as indicating a connection between the two Aischrions listed one after another; M. follows De Sanctis in considering it an error; &#7944;&#961;&#953;&#963;&#964;&#940;<ns0:supplied reason="lost">&#961;&#967;&#959;&#965;</ns0:supplied><ns0:space unit="character" extent="unknown" />, C.</ns0:note></ns0:app>
